### Get all stocks
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks

### Search stocks by name
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/search?name=Apple

### Search stocks by industry
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/search?industry=Technology

### Search stocks by symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/search?symbol=AAPL

### Search stocks with multiple criteria
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/search?name=Microsoft&industry=Technology&symbol=MSFT

### Get stock by symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/AAPL

### Get stock price
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/AAPL/price

### Get non-existent stock
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/INVALID

### Get price for non-existent stock
GET http://localhost:3000/stocks/INVALID/price
